lemma successive_end_3: "successive P (xs @ [x]) \<Longrightarrow> \<not> P x \<Longrightarrow> P y \<Longrightarrow> \<not> P z \<Longrightarrow> successive P (xs @ [x,y,z])"
by (induction _ xs rule: list_two_induct) auto
